d.\n- Required outputs:\n  - canonical method `signature` format in `data/api/electron2d-api-manifest.json` without duplicated parameter lists or duplicated `()`.\n  - RED/GREEN focused test that rejects method signatures matching duplicate call shapes such as `\\)\\(` or `\\(\\)\\(\\)`.\n  - synchronized domain document/generated manifest/docs evidence and task/diary notes.\n- Required commands:\n  - `dotnet build eng/Electron2D.Build/Electron2D.Build.csproj --no-restore -v:minimal`\n  - focused integration test for API manifest method signatures.\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build --no-build --no-restore -- update api-manifest --wiki-path .github/wiki --check`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build --no-build --no-restore -- verify api-compatibility --wiki-path .github/wiki`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build --no-build --no-restore -- verify audit-followups`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build --no-build --no-restore -- update docs --check`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build --no-build --no-restore -- verify docs`\n  - `dotnet run --project eng/Electron2D.Build --no-build --no-restore -- verify licenses` when C# source changes.\n  - `git diff --check`\n- External audit:\n  - required for final acceptance unless a parent gate explicitly owns audit evidence.\n\n### Самодостаточное описание\n\nControl audit `T-0241` r07 принял задачу, но нашёл follow-up в generated API manifest: у method entries поле `signature` содержит дублированную параметрическую часть, например `public System.Single GetPlayingSpeed()()` или `public Electron2D.Error AddAnimation(...)(...)`. Это ухудшает пригодность manifest для внешних инструментов, API сравнения и документации, но не блокировало root-contract задачу `T-0241`.\n\nОжидаемый результат: generator пишет для каждого метода ровно один канонический signature format, без повторной пары скобок и без второго списка параметров. Manifest, Wiki/API reference и тестовые фикстуры должны быть синхронизированы с новым форматом.\n\n### Internal substrate acceptance contract\n\n- Method signatures are deterministic and canonical across generated manifest entries.\n- Existing method identity, parameter metadata and API compatibility checks remain intact.\n- The fix is limited to manifest/documentation formatting and does not add, remove or implement public runtime API members.\n- The verifier/test fails closed on duplicate method call shapes in generated manifest data.\n\n### Критерии приёмки\n\n- [ ] `docs/documentation/api-manifest.md` documents the canonical method signature format.\n- [ ] Focused tests fail on duplicate shapes such as `GetPlayingSpeed()()` and `AddAnimation(...)(...)`.\n- [ ] `data/api/electron2d-api-manifest.json` has no method `signature` matching duplicated parameter-list patterns.\n- [ ] Wiki/API reference and generated docs remain synchronized after generator output changes.\n- [ ] `verify audit-followups` passes with the closure note from `T-0241` control r07.\n\n### Подзадачи\n\n- [ ] Add a RED regression for duplicate method signature call shapes in generated API manifest entries.\n- [ ] Fix `eng/Electron2D.ApiManifestGenerator/Program.cs` signature construction.\n- [ ] Regenerate API manifest and generated documentation artifacts through owning commands.\n- [ ] Update domain documentation if the public manifest contract changes.\n- [ ] Run focused tests, API manifest check, docs checks, license verifier when needed, `verify audit-followups` and `git diff --check`.\n\n### Current evidence\n\n- audit-followup-closure:\n  - source: docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0241-audit-control-r07.md\n  - id: FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F1\n  - state: tracked-new\n  - target: T-0983\n  - rationale: Control audit `T-0241` r07 accepted the current task and classified duplicate generated method signatures as a separate P1 API manifest/tooling follow-up. `T-0983` tracks a zero-context fix without expanding the accepted `T-0241` scope.\n\n### Заметки агента\n\n2026-07-06T03:26:00+03:00 - Создано как `tracked-new` closure для `FOLLOW_UP_FINDING F1` из `docs/verdicts/release-management/t-0241-audit-control-r07.md`; control r07 содержит `VERDICT: ACCEPT`, а finding не блокирует T-0241.\n\n"
